question: What is the age and population group for the most recent year for New York?
sql_query1: select MedianAge, PopulationGroup from AgeDemographics JOIN Cities ON AgeDemographics.CityId = Cities.id where Cities.CityName = 'New York' ORDER BY Year DESC LIMIT 1;
sql_query2: select AgeRange, PopulationGroup from AgeDemographics JOIN Cities ON AgeDemographics.CityId = Cities.id where Cities.CityName = 'New York' ORDER BY Year DESC LIMIT 1;
sql_query3: select MedianAge, PopulationGroup from AgeDemographics JOIN Cities ON AgeDemographics.CityId = Cities.id where Cities.CityName = 'New York' ORDER BY Year DESC LIMIT 1;
interpretation1: Give me the median age and population group for the most recent year for New York.
interpretation2: Give me the age range and population group for the most recent year for New York.
interpretation3: Give me the median age, age range and population group for the most recent year for New York.
sql_query_general: select Age, PopulationGroup from AgeDemographics JOIN Cities ON AgeDemographics.CityId = Cities.id where Cities.CityName = 'New York' ORDER BY Year DESC LIMIT 1;
